---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Verkada Products | Blue Cap IT — Gold Partner" description="Explore Verkada's 9 product lines through Blue Cap IT. Cameras, access control, air quality sensors, alarms, intercoms, command software, command connector, workplace, and connectivity. Official Gold Partner.">
  <div class="inner-hero">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="crumbs"><a href="index.html">Home</a> <span>/</span> Verkada Products</div>
      <div class="section-label">Official Verkada Gold Partner</div>
      <h1>Verkada <span class="grad">Products</span></h1>
      <p class="section-sub">Blue Cap IT sells, installs, and supports the full Verkada product line. Explore the solutions below and contact us for a free quote on any product.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="products-grid">
        <a href="cameras.html" class="product-card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;cursor:pointer;">
          <img src="/Cameras_Family_Portrait_Pillars.png" alt="Verkada Security Cameras" style="width:100%;border-radius:0.75rem;margin-bottom:1rem;" />
          <h3>Video Security Cameras</h3>
          <p>AI-powered, cloud-managed cameras with built-in storage. No NVR or on-site servers required. View footage from anywhere, on any device.</p>
          <span class="btn-primary" style="margin-top:auto;display:inline-block;">Learn More</span>
        </a>
        <a href="access-control.html" class="product-card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;cursor:pointer;">
          <img src="/241017_Access_Control_Family_hard_shadow.png" alt="Verkada Access Control" style="width:100%;border-radius:0.75rem;margin-bottom:1rem;" />
          <h3>Access Control</h3>
          <p>Cloud-based door access with mobile credentials, badge readers, and real-time management. Secure every entrance from one dashboard.</p>
          <span class="btn-primary" style="margin-top:auto;display:inline-block;">Learn More</span>
        </a>
        <a href="sensors.html" class="product-card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;cursor:pointer;">
          <img src="/air-quality-hero.png" alt="Verkada Air Quality Sensors" style="width:100%;border-radius:0.75rem;margin-bottom:1rem;" />
          <h3>Air Quality Sensors</h3>
          <p>Monitor air quality, temperature, humidity, and motion across your facilities. Get real-time alerts when conditions go out of range.</p>
          <span class="btn-primary" style="margin-top:auto;display:inline-block;">Learn More</span>
        </a>
        <a href="alarms.html" class="product-card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;cursor:pointer;">
          <img src="/250916_Alarms_Family_right_Side_2_0030.png" alt="Verkada Alarms" style="width:100%;border-radius:0.75rem;margin-bottom:1rem;" />
          <h3>Alarms &amp; Intrusion Detection</h3>
          <p>Wireless alarm panels, door and window sensors, and motion detectors — all managed through Verkada Command with professional monitoring.</p>
          <span class="btn-primary" style="margin-top:auto;display:inline-block;">Learn More</span>
        </a>
        <a href="intercom.html" class="product-card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;cursor:pointer;">
          <img src="/240919_Intercom_SH050_Trio_ALT_005_web_Still0176.png" alt="Verkada Intercoms" style="width:100%;border-radius:0.75rem;margin-bottom:1rem;" />
          <h3>Intercoms &amp; Visitor Management</h3>
          <p>Video intercoms for building entries with remote unlock, two-way audio, and visitor logs. Manage access from your phone or desktop.</p>
          <span class="btn-primary" style="margin-top:auto;display:inline-block;">Learn More</span>
        </a>
        <a href="command.html" class="product-card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;cursor:pointer;">
          <img src="/240719_Badges_Laptop_Mobile_Straight01.png" alt="Verkada Command Software" style="width:100%;border-radius:0.75rem;margin-bottom:1rem;" />
          <h3>Verkada Command</h3>
          <p>The cloud platform that ties everything together. Manage cameras, access control, sensors, alarms, and intercoms from one unified dashboard.</p>
          <span class="btn-primary" style="margin-top:auto;display:inline-block;">Learn More</span>
        </a>
        <a href="command-connector.html" class="product-card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;cursor:pointer;">
          <img src="/command-connector-hero.png" alt="Verkada Command Connector" style="width:100%;border-radius:0.75rem;margin-bottom:1rem;" />
          <h3>Command Connector</h3>
          <p>Integrate third-party and legacy cameras into Verkada Command. Keep your existing camera investment while gaining cloud management and AI analytics.</p>
          <span class="btn-primary" style="margin-top:auto;display:inline-block;">Learn More</span>
        </a>
        <a href="workplace.html" class="product-card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;cursor:pointer;">
          <img src="/workplace-hero.png" alt="Verkada Workplace" style="width:100%;border-radius:0.75rem;margin-bottom:1rem;" />
          <h3>Workplace</h3>
          <p>Digital visitor management, mailroom tracking, badge printing, and guest pre-registration — all managed through Verkada Command.</p>
          <span class="btn-primary" style="margin-top:auto;display:inline-block;">Learn More</span>
        </a>
        <a href="connectivity.html" class="product-card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;cursor:pointer;">
          <img src="/connectivity-hero.png" alt="Verkada Connectivity" style="width:100%;border-radius:0.75rem;margin-bottom:1rem;" />
          <h3>Connectivity</h3>
          <p>Cellular gateways and managed switches for reliable network connectivity. Ideal for remote sites or as backup when wired internet is unavailable.</p>
          <span class="btn-primary" style="margin-top:auto;display:inline-block;">Learn More</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="cta-band">
    <div class="section-label">Let's Talk</div>
    <h2>Ready to Explore<br/><span class="grad">Verkada Solutions?</span></h2>
    <p>Contact Blue Cap IT for a free site assessment and product recommendation. We'll help you choose the right Verkada products for your needs — with transparent pricing and expert installation.</p>
    <div class="btn-group">
      <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
      <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost">📞 (410) 858-4031</a>
      <a href="mailto:info@bluecapit.com" class="btn-ghost">✉️ info@bluecapit.com</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
